    <item>
      <title>欧盟领导人敦促“范式转变”以扭转欧洲衰落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/eu-leaders-to-urge-paradigm-shift-to-reverse-european-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟相对于主要地缘政治对手的影响力不断减弱，给欧洲各国首都敲响了警钟，迫使各国领导人讨论彻底转型，以提高欧盟在充满敌意的世界中的竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/eu-leaders-to-urge-paradigm-shift-to-reverse-european-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 18:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克罗地亚总理普伦科维奇在激烈的选举中遭遇挫折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/croatia-s-plenkovic-may-lose-majority-in-vote-exit-polls-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗地亚总理安德烈·普连科维奇在紧张的全国选举中遭遇挫折，因为他面临总统佐兰·米拉诺维奇的挑战，后者嘲笑对乌克兰的军事援助。]]></description>
